Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:11.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滾啊滾 滾啊滾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 咱們可不是堆雪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼滾雪會運得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到居然會遇險被困在雪山裡 還在這裡搭起了冰屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是在說笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得他好激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:34.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 貴志跟健吾現在都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們四個人得一起做點事才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那遇險到底有什麼危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,危險的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我們現在沒東西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾 貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遇險可真是相當危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:02.20,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:09.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:30.38,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:36.11,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.91,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.72,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.53,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.89,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.66,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:59.09,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:05.34,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.15,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:14.64,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:02.20,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:09.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:30.38,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:36.11,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.91,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.72,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.53,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.89,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.66,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:59.09,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:05.34,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.15,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:14.64,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們就在這裡等待救援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.71,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(960,960)\an8\3c&HFFFFFF&}第十二話 雪祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還得儘量保存體能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然比較艱難 但大家一定要堅持住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像會很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:44.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說 我可以一直這樣近距離地待在三島旁邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺不賴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上這麼冷的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:52.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 抱歉我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 要是他們還是不來救我們的話會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:00.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 把氣氛搞得一團糟就開溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為我說這條是近路才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是健吾的錯啦 這是大家的決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:27.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這是大家判斷的失誤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這事不賴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這反應真討打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 雛是不是有點慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 別嚇我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是救援的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在哪裡看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經出現幻象了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 有件事我希望你們替我保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我飛上天去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這回又變成妄想了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:54.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島 再怎麼說也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣獎勵她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 快醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在只能等待救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:11.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在山裡亂逛平白消耗體力的話 你可能會死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:16.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不阻止她的話 小雛她會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是我們產生幻覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們是什麼時候開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛從廁所回來之後 事情就變得不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道她去了廁所就一直沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 雛你還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經還以為你就是台造糞機器的 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我們就有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就用小雛的能力去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好餓 能力用不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那剛才的事情算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾跟貴志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他們了 你現在能用超能力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 用不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟我來一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 這之後你可以閉上眼睛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上眼就有飯吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪山裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨雪山壽司店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 你就坐這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 你要吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鮭魚子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您還真是幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的話 還能吃新鮮的魚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 鮭魚子軍艦壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:45.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼啊 這是雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客人你不要說傻話啊 這就是鮭魚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是還沒完全解凍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老闆 再多來點鮭魚子軍艦壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛你看 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你多吃點肚子就飽了 也就可以用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:29.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是山葵太辣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說鮭魚子裡是不放山葵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 你快看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看她吃得多香…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 我看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧雛 想吃多少都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,僅限鮭魚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：「想吃多少」和「鮭魚子」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺只要努力一下 就可以使用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:21.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒 我們在這兒 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:27.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 在這兒會有雪祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在扮醋薑片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別管這個了 趕快營救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這孩子真是的 老是讓我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:02.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃真正的鮭魚子 要解凍後的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能平安健康地活著我就知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去刷盤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,旅遊開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 下次杏子你也跟我們去泡溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\blur2\3c&H28A994&\c&H030053&\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H171717&\pos(390,348)}特集 當代黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\fs50\pos(410,414)\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H0D0C16&}渴求{\c&H393CB7&\3c&HFFFFFF&}血{\c&H171717&}與暴力與金錢的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1526,534)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q你們之間沒有人情世故嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是休息日 但也別睡到中午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fs80\fn思源宋体 CN\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}然後三年後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡 真是漫長的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和小雛相遇後過了快三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找到能讓我們的搖滾幻覺秀完成的線索的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聚在這裡的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:21.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來請大家觀賞超人拳法的氣功精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望入門的請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是我夢寐以求的幻覺嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像小雛那樣的不可思議力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:50.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不來學習就不能和她說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慘了 我聽不懂中文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停 暫停 my name is 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人 請不要和無關人員牽扯過多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好 my name is 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為真緒大人您是超人拳法的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}等… I am 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:10.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,I am rocker！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡包衣食住 我本以為會很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是總覺得變得越來越奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 漢服最開始是覺得挺可愛的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直穿一樣的也膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 小雛 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能穿就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:36.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就快三年了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣都想去日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來剛才那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:19.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人今天也跟木頭人用日語在碎碎念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟往常一樣啊 真是古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:29.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 聽說白天的演武有日本人混進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以防萬一 要對他加緊監視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的超人拳法 是不可以失去那個孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 小雛 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是打碎壺的那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 I am 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 接下來的話用中文怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是昨天那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 搖滾的話是世界共同的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話只要唱歌就行了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用唱也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 日語？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的樂隊「CENTRAL PARK」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是對搖滾加以幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開拓了搖滾幻覺秀這一全新音樂種類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們去了美國學習幻覺把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那裡進行的 只是魔術而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那時 我看到了你的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得「就是這個！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就想著說 我所追求的真正的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是可以用氣功再現啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想知道日本的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可能不要跟這個人說太多話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩人也覺得是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女孩子不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在跟自己製作的人偶說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪到這個地步 氣功就無法變厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還真搖滾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我接下來還有事 就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓小雛看看 沒有她我們也能做到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請教我氣功!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說「小雛」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛是指這孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 大概是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,髮色之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於… 終於有線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我來教你氣功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換 請帶我去見小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們現在都還是郵件好友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人 差不多到要回去的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我還有點話想跟這個人說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 好不容易抓到了小雛的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣被光頭佬帶回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就再也沒有機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:01.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:03.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:06.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼要逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人 你居然攻擊同門師兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全員一起上 把她抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的超能力偽裝出來的冒牌拳法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是被稱為內家拳的頂點的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手機啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是沒打電話的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 把他們都打飛就會暴露我的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣的話我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:22.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:26.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被抬手抓著而已我就浮起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺是！跟小雛的幻覺把戲相同!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是在追求這個啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說把這個皺巴巴又光溜溜的老光頭扔出去就糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別犯傻了 說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了師傅慧眼挖掘出了你的才能還有養育之恩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們用官員的關係 還為身位孤兒的你做了個身份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我的力量增加門徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收到的學費應該也不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:22.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我已經償還恩義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無妨 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在電視上被介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在全國各地建立了十個分部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這全都是真緒你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 如果你能出色地完成超人拳法的試煉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就認可你去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 難道說要把那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個至今為止都沒人成功過啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:48.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:49.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人成功過 難道說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了啊！師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無妨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:00.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:07.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 將這個鐵人利落地破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:14.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒啊 無人懷疑你的內家拳功力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:23.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 對著這個鐵人只允許用外家拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 稍微再修行一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後再去日本 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上嗎 開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:35.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 再怎麼說那個也搖滾過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:36.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把如此高速旋轉的鐵棒停下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:26.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒啊 我就允許你去日本建立分部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不論什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之要大量地拉攏客人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就是頭號弟子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧你 我應該不用困擾在日本怎麼生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 終於要邁上搖滾幻覺秀的道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:57.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 終於能跟斑鳩說我的球不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去往小雛和杏子在等待著的 日本
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:29.14,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}毎日が穏やかに過ぎてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:34.73,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}同じ日々を繰り返して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:41.70,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}なんとなく過ごしているのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:47.21,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}一緒に探そう　輝く未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:54.34,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}知らないことがたくさんで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:58.29,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}クラクラしっちゃて　あっがちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.99,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}生まれて初めてのキモチ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.26,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}大好きこころは無重力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.97,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}だんだん体をふわり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.44,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}太陽まで届きそうなぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.95,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}不思議だね　キモチ一つで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:27.24,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}こんなに見える世界が ぐっと見えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:34.01,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}新しい一日が回り出すよ
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:29.14,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}每一天都安穩地度過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:34.73,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}重複著平淡無奇的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:41.70,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}日子不知不覺就過去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:47.21,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}一起去尋找吧 那光輝的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:54.34,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}未知的事情堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:58.29,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}昏頭轉向  心情激動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.99,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}人生第一次體驗到的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.26,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}最喜歡的心情沒有重力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:10.97,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}身體慢慢變得輕飄飄了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.44,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}好像快要飛到太陽上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.95,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}這一份心情 真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:27.24,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}沒想到世界變得如此清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:34.01,hinamatsuri_edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\4c&H000000&}來開始新的一天吧
